        {
            "title": "歐洲央行管委Villeroy稱下一步舉措很可能是加息",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"Eurostat\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"585\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/T8jxft2fwh4qU.PkNifU1g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4NQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/25ba0a7c149f7a134435ad62e9a264c9\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Eurostat</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"歐洲央行\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:歐洲央行;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/歐洲央行\">歐洲央行</a>管委Francois <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Villeroy\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:Villeroy;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Villeroy\">Villeroy</a> de Galhau表示，伊朗戰爭正將歐元區經濟推向更接近央行的不利情境，這意味著下一步政策舉措很可能是加息。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「長期衝突顯然是一個負面因素，」這位法國央行行長周四在巴黎發表講話時表示。截至目前，「我們更接近中度不利情境，而非基準情境」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上述言論與Villeroy的幾位同事看法一致。他們認為，經過近五周的中東戰事，能源成本上漲將持續影響歐洲的消費者價格。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-58bce5d3-037a-3d93-81f3-ac53d2371b98-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">3月歐元區通膨率創自2022年俄羅斯入侵烏克蘭以來的最大增幅，與此同時，隨著川普威脅進一步升級戰事，各國政府和央行已開始下調對經濟活動的預期。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"585\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Ys70hcoZqg4aLAiNyVaceA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4NQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/efbd0cf4136e967167d4d8d339bb970e\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管面臨這些不利因素，Villeroy稱現在判斷何時應該收緊貨幣政策還為時過早。他還表示，歐元區目前的處境比四年前好得多，現階段的情況不會重蹈覆轍。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「現在預測歐洲央行加息時間表還為時尚早，」Villeroy表示，「但很顯然，我們有能力在必要時採取任何行動。顯然，關鍵利率的下一次變動極有可能是上調。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">投資者押注今年歐洲央行可能加息三次，並預計本月晚些時候加息的可能性較高。歐洲央行下一次利率決議將於4月30日公佈。這將是Villeroy最後一次參加歐洲央行會議，他此前宣布將在第二個任期結束之前離任。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">將存款利率從目前的2%提高，將有助於控制通膨預期——Villeroy表示，歐洲央行正在密切關注家庭、企業和市場的情況。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「這一次，如果事實證明是必要的，我們會毫不猶豫地採取行動，」他說。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Villeroy Says Economy Now Closer to ECB’s Adverse Scenario</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E7%AE%A1%E5%A7%94villeroy%E7%A8%B1%E4%B8%8B-%E6%AD%A5%E8%88%89%E6%8E%AA%E5%BE%88%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E6%98%AF%E5%8A%A0%E6%81%AF-172347415.html",
